    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">431 Stevens Street</name>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1878-07-12">July 12<ptr target="loc.04033_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My dear Reid</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I forward you same mail with this the little "Passage to India" we spoke of, with the "Captain" bit in.</p>
            
            <p>If convenient have the pay for my letter of July 4 in <hi rend="italic">Tribune</hi> ($20) sent me here.<ptr target="loc.04033_n2"/></p>
            
            <p>I am well, for me&#8212;All the better for my pleasant NY jaunt.</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
